item.name: Upgrade 4.2.4 - 4.3.1
item.description:
This major release includes significant optimizations that give a massive speed boost (92/100 by Google PageSpeed). The release also introduces a new add-on Blog which allows you to create a blog inside your store, an ability to create a mini-store for a vendor (Multi-Vendor only), export/import of option combinations, a refined Upgrade center which makes the future upgrades safer and faster, and more. Check the changelog for all improvements and bug fixes.

Read our blog to learn more
